### Get list of drivers
GET {{api}}/driver
Authorization: {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get list of drivers filtering
POST {{api}}/driver/filter?full=true
Authorization: {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"isReady": false
}

### Get single driver by id
GET {{api}}/driver/{{driverId}}?full=true
Authorization: {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

