### Upload driver avatar
POST {{api}}/driver/avatar/{{driverId}}
Authorization: {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="avatar.png"

